                The Minister of State (Mr. McNeil)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-85b58f9d-f749-40c4-9c9d-c4dc15992895" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
