        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-e9e06f98-d33c-408a-9234-a54f9e6e7927'>
            
<p class=""><em>It being Four o'Clock, the Motion for the Adjournment of the House lapsed, without Question put</em>.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
