<p class="">They have not yet reached the Library.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-670ddcd5-7225-479d-bdcc-2be824aa9429" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
